      <title>中国称菲律宾船只“非法”登陆有争议的环礁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-illegally-landed-disputed-atoll-2024-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周六表示，一艘来自菲律宾的小型民用船只“非法停泊在两国声称拥有主权的南海环礁的海滩上”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-illegally-landed-disputed-atoll-2024-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 06:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜于2月2日试射巡航导弹-朝中社</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-tested-firing-cruise-missiles-feb-2-kcna-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方媒体周六报道称，朝鲜于 2 月 2 日在西海岸试射了巡航导弹和新型陆对空导弹，证实了一系列旨在增强防御能力的武器发射。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-tested-firing-cruise-missiles-feb-2-kcna-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 21:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒大电动汽车暂停与迪拜 NWTN 就重新起草协议进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/evergrande-ev-unit-suspends-talks-with-dubais-nwtn-redrafting-deal-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国恒大新能源汽车 (NEV) 周五表示，已暂停与迪拜出行公司 NWTN 签订的价值 38.9 亿港元（合 4.9742 亿美元）的股份认购协议条款的修订谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/evergrande-ev-unit-suspends-talks-with-dubais-nwtn-redrafting-deal-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰扩大与斯洛伐克的边境管制以阻止非法移民</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-extends-border-controls-with-slovakia-stem-illegal-migration-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰内政部周五表示，波兰已将与斯洛伐克的边境管制延长至 3 月 2 日，以阻止非法移民从斯洛伐克领土进入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-extends-border-controls-with-slovakia-stem-illegal-migration-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：阿里巴巴考虑出售包括盒马鲜生、大润发在内的消费资产——消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibaba-considers-sale-consumer-assets-including-freshippo-rt-mart-sources-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位知情人士称，中国互联网巨头阿里巴巴集团正在寻求出售多项消费行业资产，包括食品杂货业务盒马鲜生和零售商大润发。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibaba-considers-sale-consumer-assets-including-freshippo-rt-mart-sources-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 13:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦化学袭击造成数人受伤，警方正在追捕一名男子</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-police-launch-manhunt-after-chemical-attack-leaves-several-injured-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方正在搜捕一名涉嫌向多人投掷腐蚀性化学品致伤的男子，而他在性侵犯定罪后获得庇护的身份给该案增添了政治因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-police-launch-manhunt-after-chemical-attack-leaves-several-injured-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 11:25:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举前一周，巴基斯坦军方在俾路支省打死 24 名武装分子</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-military-kills-24-militants-balochistan-week-before-elections-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦军方周五在一份声明中表示，距离全国选举还不到一周，巴基斯坦军方三天内在动荡的西南部俾路支省打死了 24 名武装分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-military-kills-24-militants-balochistan-week-before-elections-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 10:56:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国专家要求菲律宾对媒体杀戮采取行动，废除反共工作组</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/un-expert-tells-philippines-act-media-killings-abolish-anti-communist-task-force-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联合国专家周五敦促菲律宾采取更多措施遏制杀害记者的行为，并支持废除一个反共工作组，该工作组的行动压制了活动人士的言论自由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/un-expert-tells-philippines-act-media-killings-abolish-anti-communist-task-force-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 09:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第五招：龙争虎斗</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-graphic-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的龙年即将到来，但世界第二大经济体目前并没有蓬勃发展，而央行行长的强硬言论也让投资者对降息即将到来的缓解信心不足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-graphic-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 08:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚称印尼进口许可证延误正在影响农产品贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-says-indonesian-import-permit-delays-are-hitting-agricultural-trade-2024-02-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚政府周五表示，印度尼西亚延迟发放一系列农产品进口许可证，影响了澳大利亚和其他国家的发货。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-says-indonesian-import-permit-delays-are-hitting-agricultural-trade-2024-02-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 08:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
